        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2026</div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h2 class="timeline-title">Backend with Node.js &amp; Express</h2>
            <p class="timeline-body">
              Built REST APIs, practiced routing, middleware, and deployment-ready folder
              structures using Node.js and Express.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2026</div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h2 class="timeline-title">Software Engineering Degree</h2>
