              Core subjects in algorithms, data structures, software architecture, and databases,
              building a strong foundation for backend and web development.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
          <div class="timeline-card">
            <h2 class="timeline-title">Web Development Fundamentals</h2>
            <p class="timeline-body">
              HTML, CSS, and JavaScript fundamentals with an emphasis on layout, accessibility, and
              responsive design patterns.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
